APPENING!\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\ud83d\udd90\ufe0f", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2048916553664450604", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZaTkz6j", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 108, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8586765, "raw_content": "", "author": "MEME-SUPREME", "created": 1777386186198, "profile_picture": "in2RwAS4UU0c", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Scot", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZaTkz6j.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/ginamilan_/status/2048916553664450604?s=20", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "18-year-old Nikita Casap from Wisconsin was found guilty three months ago of murdering his parents to steal their money for his plan to assassinate President Trump. He left their bodies to rot in the house for weeks. Then he fled across the country, bought drones and explosives, wrote a manifesto...", "last_comment_created": 1777391755585, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 5, "score_up": 108, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": [{"width": 1584, "heightRatio": 77, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HG82vr_aQAAi1x_.jpg", "height": 1224}], "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 283, "created": 1777334748000, "id": "2048916553664450604", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1846366445774467072/3ZOrWKeh_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Gina Milan", "username": "ginamilan_"}, "content": "18-year-old Nikita Casap from Wisconsin was found guilty three months ago of murdering his parents to steal their money for his plan to assassinate President Trump.\n\nHe left their bodies to rot in the house for weeks. Then he fled across the country, bought drones and explosives,", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 11169}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZaTjsyl", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 191, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8586377, "raw_content": "Imagine you travel to Chicago and accidentally end up on the south side, maybe took the wrong train or the wrong turn.\n\nThey could kill you and the chances that somebody would be held responsible are less than 3%.\n\nThe 2025 clearance rate for Chicago shows that only in 24% of homicides there was a suspect charged with a crime. At the same time black juries have only a 12% conviction rate against black defendants.\n\nhttps://heyjackass.com/2025-homicide-clearance-rate/\n\nhttps://nitter.net/wallstreetapes/status/1960570206281195669\n\nThat works out to a chance of only 2.88% for a conviction. Of course, that is assuming that the police did their work perfectly and charged the right person for the crime.\n", "author": "TheLawofOne-", "created": 1777374646469, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "God-is-good", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "I've begun to realize that in the USA the law essentially does not apply to black people", "last_comment_created": 1777391115207, "content": "<p>Imagine you travel to Chicago and accidentally end up on the south side, maybe took the wrong train or the wrong turn.</p>\n<p>They could kill you and the chances that somebody would be held responsible are less than 3%.</p>\n<p>The 2025 clearance rate for Chicago shows that only in 24% of homicides there was a suspect charged with a crime. At the same time black juries have only a 12% conviction rate against black defendants.</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://heyjackass.com/2025-homicide-clearance-rate/\" target=\"_blank\">https://heyjackass.com/2025-homicide-clearance-rate/</a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://nitter.net/wallstreetapes/status/1960570206281195669\" target=\"_blank\">https://nitter.net/wallstreetapes/status/1960570206281195669</a></p>\n<p>That works out to a chance of only 2.88% for a conviction. Of course, that is assuming that the police did their work perfectly and charged the right person for the crime.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 13, "score_up": 191, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2049131612835586505", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZaUrS5M", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 74, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8587034, "raw_content": "", "author": "KuzoKevin", "created": 1777392880435, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Ol5nDimer", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZaUrS5M.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/SecRollins/status/2049131612835586505", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "In just ONE state, 14,000 indi